docs/

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json

# Ignore vscode AI rules
.github/instructions/codacy.instructions.md
.graphifyignore
